{"tid":1115521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何面對孤獨","createTime":"2019-04-19T08:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T08:13:15.000Z","uid":241448,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7321dea56ead989fb9fa0155643b9f19c709535b","tid":1115521,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"唔識行出去建立新圈子，又唔識面對孤獨既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明由細到大都係毒撚一個最開心，點解宜家會愈黎愈焦慮，生活冇左目標咁。覺得唔可以咁樣繼續落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又唔鐘意埋堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己都覺得好煩"},{"pid":"4ec440d77c3e96fabc2a41a7e5506c6f85b53ccb","tid":1115521,"uid":53515,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"當你學識獨處，啲人就自然想識你，到時你就覺得人群好麻煩"},{"pid":"40315c67cd90773db540d630f8ade845c2e42d6d","tid":1115521,"uid":89558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"冇嫁喇 你咪諗下點樣係孤獨入面尋找快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申過來人"},{"pid":"6be3fde1d2972d02f49eb5b5b9475fbfdcb9d56e","tid":1115521,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec440d77c3e96fabc2a41a7e5506c6f85b53ccb","tid":1115521,"uid":53515,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"當你學識獨處，啲人就自然想識你，到時你就覺得人群好麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇乜人想識我，我都唔想識人，冇咩野岩傾，亦都好難同人相處。想搵啲野閉關修練提升自己，但收工好攰只想打機做廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66fc064bf6bb9cb0aee4ae78a9f8e6e3ade84ef","tid":1115521,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40315c67cd90773db540d630f8ade845c2e42d6d","tid":1115521,"uid":89558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"冇嫁喇 你咪諗下點樣係孤獨入面尋找快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkg